{}.response: This API requires a SPAC symbol as input to retrieve the latest SEC filings related to a specific Special Purpose Acquisition Company (SPAC). The response would typically include details such as the filing date, document type, description of the filing, and a link to the full document on the SEC website. Without a specific SPAC symbol, we are unable to provide the relevant SEC filings. Please provide a SPAC symbol as input to use this function effectively.
